WEBVTT

01:44.340 --> 01:48.800
[A LOVER IN THE MORTAL WORLD]

01:49.530 --> 01:51.590
[Episode 3]

01:57.229 --> 01:58.229
Guys,

01:59.350 --> 02:00.590
bring me more wine.

02:00.760 --> 02:02.760
Your Majesty, you're in a good mood.

02:03.280 --> 02:04.280
Sister,

02:04.840 --> 02:05.840
why are you here?

02:06.480 --> 02:07.950
I knew you were out of wine,

02:08.210 --> 02:09.479
so I brought you some.

02:10.190 --> 02:11.870
You are so kind to me.

02:14.030 --> 02:14.840
Sister,

02:15.520 --> 02:16.360
I

02:17.680 --> 02:18.520
toast you.

02:19.030 --> 02:20.310
You have grown up.

02:21.030 --> 02:22.760
Learned to drown your sorrows.

02:23.360 --> 02:24.150
No.

02:24.710 --> 02:25.560
Okay.

02:26.430 --> 02:27.360
I

02:27.890 --> 02:29.350
will have a drink with you.

02:39.870 --> 02:41.680
What's up, Your Majesty?

02:42.960 --> 02:44.310
The sky is so beautiful.

02:44.960 --> 02:46.240
And there is good wine.

02:47.280 --> 02:48.680
But you seem

02:48.680 --> 02:49.960
in low spirits.

02:50.360 --> 02:52.079
With you here,

02:52.800 --> 02:54.530
nothing could make me unhappy.

02:55.190 --> 02:57.240
I raised you since you were little.

02:57.360 --> 02:58.590
I know your feelings

02:58.750 --> 03:00.240
at a glance.

03:00.800 --> 03:02.000
You don't have to

03:02.150 --> 03:03.800
hide anything from me.

03:04.190 --> 03:06.240
Just tell me what happened.

03:06.710 --> 03:07.520
Sister,

03:08.600 --> 03:09.230
do you

03:09.960 --> 03:11.400
ever think

03:13.510 --> 03:16.070
I am not cut out to be an emperor?

03:19.470 --> 03:20.200
Why would you

03:21.030 --> 03:22.430
think that suddenly?

03:23.560 --> 03:25.420
When our father was on the throne,

03:25.680 --> 03:28.150
his majesty and decisiveness

03:28.520 --> 03:30.430
made all the subjects

03:30.430 --> 03:32.079
submit to him.

03:33.520 --> 03:34.800
But I think...

03:36.310 --> 03:37.470
I can't do that.

03:41.840 --> 03:43.560
You just ascended the throne.

03:44.280 --> 03:46.590
Naturally, you can't

03:46.590 --> 03:48.190
compare with him right away.

03:48.710 --> 03:50.150
But I believe

03:50.840 --> 03:51.870
one day,

03:52.040 --> 03:53.970
you will awe the subjects

03:54.000 --> 03:55.280
like our father.

03:55.300 --> 03:57.610
But I don't want to awe them at all.

03:58.360 --> 03:59.800
I always feel that

04:01.190 --> 04:02.630
a high position

04:03.400 --> 04:05.460
comes with heavy responsibilities.

04:05.470 --> 04:06.720
The court

04:07.030 --> 04:09.440
should be united.

04:11.670 --> 04:13.160
Are you worried

04:13.630 --> 04:15.160
that the veteran officials

04:15.910 --> 04:16.769
are hard to control?

04:16.769 --> 04:18.180
I need to consult

04:18.390 --> 04:20.800
them about something,

04:21.870 --> 04:22.600
but…

04:23.160 --> 04:25.720
But you don't like them
dominating the court.

04:31.920 --> 04:34.320
These three veterans, Zhang, Wang, and Li,

04:34.610 --> 04:36.470
have always assisted our father.

04:37.159 --> 04:38.550
In the court,

04:38.630 --> 04:39.960
they are deeply rooted.

04:40.140 --> 04:41.700
Father also entrusted you to their care.

04:41.700 --> 04:42.770
I know that

04:42.990 --> 04:46.730
since you just ascended the throne,
you haven't wielded absolute power.

04:46.730 --> 04:47.620
But

04:49.370 --> 04:51.610
I will always be by your side

04:52.120 --> 04:53.480
and assist you.

04:56.400 --> 04:57.840
You are so kind to me.

05:02.010 --> 05:02.760
Come on.

05:05.090 --> 05:05.800
Come on.

05:07.070 --> 05:08.390
I believe in you.

05:08.410 --> 05:10.810
You will definitely revitalize the court,

05:10.900 --> 05:12.560
bring honor to the Liu family,

05:13.080 --> 05:14.930
and restore our father's glory.

05:16.310 --> 05:17.120
Okay.

05:18.610 --> 05:20.320
Since you said so,

05:21.160 --> 05:23.390
I won't let you

05:23.750 --> 05:25.680
and our father down.

05:38.720 --> 05:39.400
Fei Zheng.

05:40.550 --> 05:41.230
Tell me.

05:42.690 --> 05:44.690
How did we become enemies?

05:46.830 --> 05:47.680
Indeed.

06:08.790 --> 06:09.990
The two

06:10.480 --> 06:12.240
seem to be a good match.

06:18.070 --> 06:19.070
Sister.

06:20.790 --> 06:23.470
I really miss when we were little.

06:24.070 --> 06:25.310
Back then,

06:25.600 --> 06:26.930
Mother was still alive.

06:27.480 --> 06:28.920
Our whole family

06:30.060 --> 06:32.180
was together.

06:33.880 --> 06:35.640
Times flies.

06:37.720 --> 06:38.960
You and I

06:39.750 --> 06:43.010
should take on the responsibility
Father entrusted to us.

07:32.950 --> 07:35.750
-What are you doing here?
-What are you doing here?

07:36.130 --> 07:37.730
How would I know why I'm here?

07:39.370 --> 07:41.080
You drank too much yesterday.

07:43.260 --> 07:45.280
You look more like the one
who drank too much.

07:45.280 --> 07:46.690
Yesterday, you were

07:46.840 --> 07:48.840
yelling and screaming all the time.

07:50.790 --> 07:52.710
I was drunk all day yesterday?

07:53.030 --> 07:53.830
That's right.

07:57.830 --> 07:58.390
Did I

07:58.630 --> 07:59.830
make a fool of myself?

08:00.190 --> 08:01.190
What do you think?

08:04.510 --> 08:05.310
I...

08:07.390 --> 08:09.830
Why did you send me
a jar of wine that night?

08:09.920 --> 08:10.600
I...

08:10.800 --> 08:13.070
I gave you a jar of wine to send you off.

08:13.480 --> 08:15.410
I didn't expect you to get so drunk.

08:16.710 --> 08:18.150
I don't usually drink.

08:18.220 --> 08:20.680
How would I know
what I'm like when I'm drunk?

08:25.920 --> 08:27.850
Did you have a good time last night?

08:29.070 --> 08:29.870
Who are you?

08:30.800 --> 08:32.320
You drank so much
that you lost your memory?

08:32.320 --> 08:34.070
You don't remember
what happened yesterday at all?

08:34.070 --> 08:35.309
We met yesterday?

08:35.490 --> 08:36.450
More than that.

08:37.240 --> 08:37.880
Actually,

08:38.620 --> 08:39.830
you have to thank me.

08:40.480 --> 08:41.549
What for?

08:41.640 --> 08:43.370
I asked him to keep you in the mansion

08:43.370 --> 08:45.340
until his chronic illness is cured.

08:45.340 --> 08:46.400
He also promised to

08:46.490 --> 08:47.820
take you to the capital.

08:47.910 --> 08:48.670
Really?

08:49.270 --> 08:49.820
Zheng.

08:50.100 --> 08:51.370
When did I ever say that?

08:51.370 --> 08:52.800
I can testify.

08:53.250 --> 08:53.710
Really.

08:54.060 --> 08:54.820
That's great.

08:54.820 --> 08:55.490
Come in.

09:00.720 --> 09:02.360
This is Imperial Physician Li.

09:02.360 --> 09:03.360
He came here today

09:03.380 --> 09:05.170
to learn from you

09:05.360 --> 09:07.580
how to treat General Xiao's
chronic illness.

09:07.580 --> 09:08.580
I wonder if you

09:08.610 --> 09:10.210
could demonstrate it for us.

09:10.480 --> 09:11.120
Now?

09:11.390 --> 09:12.150
Now.

09:12.550 --> 09:13.360
Now?

09:14.250 --> 09:15.130
Right now.

10:04.420 --> 10:05.350
Lord Fei.

10:05.370 --> 10:06.010
How is it?

10:06.750 --> 10:08.930
The General's pulse is
both weak and strong,

10:08.930 --> 10:10.500
floating on the outside
but sinking inside.

10:10.500 --> 10:13.390
It seems a warm current
is spreading through his body.

10:13.390 --> 10:15.270
I think General has coughed

10:15.290 --> 10:16.770
much less recently.

10:16.800 --> 10:19.600
I didn't expect you to
know so much about medicine.

10:20.630 --> 10:23.120
I have served the royal family
for many years.

10:23.120 --> 10:25.390
I have some skill in taking pulses.

10:26.030 --> 10:28.550
But if you want to
cure the General's illness,

10:28.550 --> 10:30.080
acupuncture is not enough.

10:30.150 --> 10:32.120
He also needs medicine to recuperate.

10:32.120 --> 10:33.720
Among the many ingredients,

10:33.720 --> 10:35.320
the Snow Lotus

10:35.320 --> 10:37.390
is the hardest to find.

10:38.690 --> 10:39.290
Of course.

10:39.600 --> 10:40.840
The Snow Lotus is...

10:40.970 --> 10:41.570
By the way.

10:42.020 --> 10:42.820
Your medicine

10:42.970 --> 10:44.700
seems to be missing Snow Lotus.

10:45.120 --> 10:46.180
If we can't find it,

10:46.400 --> 10:47.880
all previous treatments

10:47.960 --> 10:49.750
will be in vain.

10:51.840 --> 10:54.320
When treating someone before,

10:54.320 --> 10:56.520
it seemed that I also needed Snow Lotus.

11:00.620 --> 11:01.990
Forget it. Forget it.

11:02.570 --> 11:04.150
But this old imperial doctor

11:04.150 --> 11:06.240
can write the same
prescription as me.

11:06.240 --> 11:08.150
It shows your medical skills
are excellent.

11:08.150 --> 11:08.670
My Lord.

11:09.260 --> 11:10.920
This lady's medical practice

11:11.130 --> 11:12.870
is very much like that of

11:12.940 --> 11:15.400
the head imperial physician
many years ago.

11:15.630 --> 11:16.700
She can cure

11:16.720 --> 11:19.290
the General's illness alone.

11:19.440 --> 11:22.630
May I ask who you learned
your medical skills from?

11:23.900 --> 11:24.970
I

11:27.200 --> 11:29.130
taught myself from medical books.

11:29.440 --> 11:30.770
The younger generation

11:30.840 --> 11:32.510
will surpass us in time.

11:34.170 --> 11:35.020
Farewell.

11:38.990 --> 11:41.690
The marriage alliance procession
will enter the pass soon.

11:41.690 --> 11:42.690
General Xiao,

11:43.020 --> 11:43.900
get ready.

11:44.210 --> 11:45.340
Don't worry, Zheng.

11:57.630 --> 11:58.630
This carriage is so big.

11:58.630 --> 11:59.480
It's so grand.

11:59.480 --> 12:00.240
Too grand.

12:00.240 --> 12:01.150
And too precious.

12:01.150 --> 12:02.030
Yes.

13:04.210 --> 13:06.790
[General's Mansion]

13:21.040 --> 13:22.440
[Princess of Changmo, Jiang Wanyu]

13:32.420 --> 13:33.300
Jin Xi.

13:35.130 --> 13:35.860
Here you are.

13:37.380 --> 13:38.380
What is this?

13:38.590 --> 13:40.050
Though you are my patient,

13:40.220 --> 13:42.530
I have regarded you as my sister.

13:42.950 --> 13:43.500
This is

13:43.890 --> 13:46.090
the prescription I'm giving you.

13:46.550 --> 13:48.100
If you get hurt again,

13:48.130 --> 13:50.590
you can get the medicine
and treat yourself.

13:53.140 --> 13:56.070
Three years ago, Jin Xi left
without saying goodbye.

13:56.390 --> 13:58.590
How did she become the Princess's maid?

14:02.120 --> 14:03.370
Please stop, my lords.

14:03.370 --> 14:04.970
Her Highness is taking a nap.

14:05.010 --> 14:05.860
Who are you?

14:06.020 --> 14:08.530
I am the female official
of Her Highness for the marriage alliance.

14:08.530 --> 14:10.260
General, you can call me Jin Xi.

14:11.150 --> 14:12.010
I didn't expect

14:12.310 --> 14:13.610
the female official from Changmo

14:13.610 --> 14:15.060
to be so full of energy.

14:15.520 --> 14:16.920
Her Highness is about to get married soon.

14:16.920 --> 14:18.430
Then why such negligence?

14:18.480 --> 14:19.940
Her Highness is of noble birth.

14:19.940 --> 14:22.090
The journey to Tianlang Pass
was exhausting.

14:22.090 --> 14:23.150
She wants to sleep a little longer,

14:23.150 --> 14:24.940
and I'm sure you lords can understand.

14:24.940 --> 14:27.240
Besides, guards have already been posted.

14:27.240 --> 14:29.120
What do you lords want now?

14:29.450 --> 14:30.910
It's a misunderstanding.

14:31.000 --> 14:31.910
Posting guards

14:32.320 --> 14:33.980
is for Her Highness's safety.

14:34.290 --> 14:35.820
We want to meet Her Highness

14:35.930 --> 14:37.570
simply to follow protocol.

14:37.690 --> 14:39.410
Once the relevant matters are settled,

14:39.410 --> 14:42.050
we can depart for the capital
as soon as possible.

14:42.050 --> 14:44.070
And Her Highness
can meet His Majesty sooner.

14:44.070 --> 14:44.600
That way,

14:45.140 --> 14:46.770
the marriage alliance will be perfect.

14:46.770 --> 14:47.930
My Lady,

14:48.100 --> 14:49.030
don't you agree?

14:49.380 --> 14:50.140
Jin Xi,

14:50.450 --> 14:51.340
let them in.

14:51.500 --> 14:52.020
Yes.

14:56.860 --> 14:58.020
Princess Peace.

14:58.380 --> 14:59.500
It's a nice title.

14:59.810 --> 15:01.020
My father hopes that

15:01.020 --> 15:04.020
Changmo and Jinglan
are close and friendly countries

15:04.290 --> 15:05.340
with no more wars.

15:05.410 --> 15:07.140
That is why he chose this title.

15:10.980 --> 15:12.640
Please take a look, General Xiao.

15:12.640 --> 15:13.430
No need.

15:14.620 --> 15:16.140
The royal genealogy might be real,

15:16.140 --> 15:17.480
but the person might not be.

15:17.480 --> 15:19.260
Please take off your veil, Your Highness,

15:19.260 --> 15:20.690
and let us see your true face.

15:20.690 --> 15:22.420
Your concerns are reasonable.

15:23.770 --> 15:25.170
Help me take off the veil.

15:25.380 --> 15:25.860
Yes.

15:39.220 --> 15:39.930
Lord Fei.

15:40.190 --> 15:41.790
According to the marriage
alliance process,

15:41.790 --> 15:42.990
what is the next step?

15:44.300 --> 15:45.060
Body search.

15:47.620 --> 15:48.340
Doctor Han,

15:48.340 --> 15:48.980
Miss Han,

15:48.980 --> 15:49.860
Madam Han,

15:49.860 --> 15:51.020
please help me.

15:51.380 --> 15:53.110
I'm here to treat your general.

15:53.220 --> 15:54.450
I'm not a maid in the mansion.

15:54.450 --> 15:56.100
Isn't treating his illness
and saving his life enough?

15:56.100 --> 15:57.410
He still wants to order me around.

15:57.410 --> 15:57.900
Would he dare?

15:57.900 --> 15:58.680
He wouldn't dare.

15:58.680 --> 15:59.770
He wouldn't dare order you around.

15:59.770 --> 16:01.050
He... He is begging for your help.

16:01.050 --> 16:02.220
If he wanted my help,

16:02.570 --> 16:03.780
why didn't he come himself?

16:03.780 --> 16:04.260
He...

16:05.320 --> 16:07.320
He thinks his relationship with you

16:07.340 --> 16:08.600
isn't as close as ours.

16:09.050 --> 16:10.780
She is the Princess of Changmo.

16:11.050 --> 16:12.380
Searching a Princess

16:12.650 --> 16:14.290
isn't something commoners like us can do.

16:14.290 --> 16:15.620
No matter what,

16:15.620 --> 16:16.710
you both are women.

16:17.020 --> 16:17.620
Physician Han,

16:17.620 --> 16:18.620
help me!

16:18.620 --> 16:20.550
Otherwise, I can't finish my task.

16:22.570 --> 16:23.290
All right.

16:23.620 --> 16:24.980
I'll do it as a favor to you.

16:24.980 --> 16:26.180
Thank you. Thank you.

16:27.350 --> 16:27.980
Lead the way.

16:27.980 --> 16:28.440
Please.

16:30.810 --> 16:31.610
I'll go first.

16:35.890 --> 16:36.500
General,

16:36.560 --> 16:37.820
Physician Han is here.

16:43.730 --> 16:44.330
Thank you.

16:44.930 --> 16:45.930
Then don't forget

16:46.170 --> 16:47.620
to repay me, General Xiao.

16:47.620 --> 16:48.350
Definitely.

16:52.260 --> 16:53.320
How could it be her?

16:53.690 --> 16:55.500
Later, search her thoroughly

16:55.500 --> 16:56.380
for things

16:57.260 --> 16:58.610
like silver needles, a short sword,

16:58.610 --> 16:59.410
or poison.

17:00.840 --> 17:01.570
Understood.

17:05.170 --> 17:06.700
Greetings, Your Highness.

17:06.730 --> 17:07.540
Who is this?

17:07.819 --> 17:09.099
This is Physician Han.

17:09.730 --> 17:10.839
She is also from Changmo, like you.

17:10.839 --> 17:12.020
Having her search Your Highness

17:12.020 --> 17:13.380
wouldn't be disrespectful to you.

17:13.380 --> 17:14.569
To serve Your Highness

17:14.569 --> 17:15.569
is my honor.

17:21.170 --> 17:23.619
A body search inevitably
requires taking off clothes.

17:23.619 --> 17:25.349
Are you two planning to sit here

17:25.450 --> 17:26.319
and watch?

17:27.250 --> 17:28.180
If I don't watch,

17:28.210 --> 17:29.060
how do I know

17:29.060 --> 17:30.280
if you search carefully?

17:30.280 --> 17:31.480
If you don't trust me,

17:31.820 --> 17:32.750
then I'll leave.

17:32.880 --> 17:33.580
Physician Han.

17:33.580 --> 17:34.380
Wait a moment.

17:53.860 --> 17:55.360
How could
the dignified Princess of Changmo

17:55.360 --> 17:57.250
carry anything bad?

17:57.690 --> 17:59.550
There's no need for a body search.

18:00.740 --> 18:02.470
However, this female official

18:04.730 --> 18:06.730
needs to be thoroughly checked.

18:07.060 --> 18:08.690
Why should you search me?

18:08.690 --> 18:10.350
If you don't let me search you,

18:10.410 --> 18:12.010
those men outside

18:12.010 --> 18:13.380
will have to do it.

18:15.140 --> 18:16.410
Since I must be searched,

18:16.410 --> 18:17.820
go ahead, Physician Han.

18:20.450 --> 18:21.100
Okay.

18:21.540 --> 18:22.540
Pardon me.

18:31.860 --> 18:32.820
Come in.

18:42.630 --> 18:43.630
What did you find?

18:43.730 --> 18:45.450
A dignified peace-making princess

18:45.450 --> 18:47.510
wouldn't bring anything forbidden.

18:47.860 --> 18:49.380
Not to mention the princess,

18:49.380 --> 18:51.540
I even searched her personal maid.

18:51.860 --> 18:53.100
I found nothing.

18:53.380 --> 18:54.690
It is you

18:55.170 --> 18:56.580
who are being petty.

18:59.820 --> 19:00.930
Pardon my intrusion.

19:00.930 --> 19:02.860
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

19:03.380 --> 19:05.180
Lord Fei is just doing your duty.

19:05.730 --> 19:07.650
Besides, this physician
did everything properly,

19:07.650 --> 19:09.250
so there is no offense taken.

19:13.780 --> 19:15.140
What do you think

19:15.330 --> 19:17.260
about the peace-making princess?

19:17.340 --> 19:18.710
I didn't expect Changmo barbarians

19:18.710 --> 19:19.660
to have

19:19.860 --> 19:20.930
such a princess.

19:22.300 --> 19:24.540
But the female official beside her...

19:26.650 --> 19:28.450
What about the female official?

19:29.460 --> 19:31.450
We are high-ranking officials of Jinglan.

19:31.450 --> 19:32.970
Her Highness is well-informed,

19:32.970 --> 19:35.570
but this female official
didn't panic either.

19:35.730 --> 19:36.460
She must have

19:36.890 --> 19:38.240
been through a lot.

19:40.580 --> 19:41.300
What else?

19:41.930 --> 19:43.330
She's a female official.

19:43.450 --> 19:44.990
The princess's dowry officials

19:44.990 --> 19:46.520
don't need to do heavy work.

19:46.650 --> 19:49.710
But she seems to have
removed the calluses on her hands.

19:51.020 --> 19:53.480
I didn't expect you
to observe so carefully.

19:53.580 --> 19:56.140
Changmo has been sending
spies to our country for years.

19:56.140 --> 19:57.690
I've been fighting them for years.

19:57.690 --> 19:58.820
I did many different things

19:58.820 --> 20:00.060
from a relaxed official like you

20:00.060 --> 20:02.340
who stays in the court every day.

20:04.010 --> 20:04.690
Okay.

20:05.490 --> 20:06.340
Then，

20:06.820 --> 20:08.620
how do you plan to deal with them?

20:08.820 --> 20:09.930
Didn't I just say?

20:10.000 --> 20:10.630
Tonight,

20:10.650 --> 20:11.720
you should have a drink with the princess.

20:11.720 --> 20:12.510
Me?

20:13.860 --> 20:14.930
Why?

20:15.060 --> 20:15.930
As a host,

20:16.210 --> 20:18.210
treating guests from afar to a meal

20:18.350 --> 20:19.380
is normal.

20:19.780 --> 20:20.980
And I've always known

20:21.130 --> 20:21.710
Lord Fei

20:21.780 --> 20:23.650
can hold your liquor.

20:24.380 --> 20:25.650
Why do I feel like

20:25.650 --> 20:27.310
you're not telling the truth?

20:28.620 --> 20:29.780
People tell the truth after drinking.

20:29.780 --> 20:31.340
I will host the banquet,
and you can drink with them.

20:31.340 --> 20:33.450
That's a chance to investigate the spies.

20:33.450 --> 20:34.340
Seize it.

20:38.490 --> 20:39.350
Your Highness,

20:39.540 --> 20:41.070
you're slacking off again.

20:41.820 --> 20:43.390
It's just you and me here.

20:43.730 --> 20:45.060
Who am I performing for?

20:45.210 --> 20:46.810
Sit down and rest for a while.

20:47.730 --> 20:49.190
That's against the rules.

20:49.250 --> 20:50.250
Rules. Rules.

20:50.690 --> 20:51.950
All you know are rules.

20:52.170 --> 20:52.970
So annoying.

20:55.970 --> 20:57.970
I wish Liu Chu were the sort of person

20:57.970 --> 21:00.370
who doesn't follow the rules,
just like me.

21:03.840 --> 21:04.810
Jin Xi.

21:06.340 --> 21:08.210
You've been with me for so many years.

21:08.210 --> 21:10.070
Why haven't I ever seen you smile?

21:10.410 --> 21:12.340
There's nothing to be happy about.

21:12.340 --> 21:14.940
But if we could leave
for the capital tomorrow,

21:15.210 --> 21:16.410
then I might smile.

21:17.300 --> 21:18.970
I don't want to go that early.

21:19.410 --> 21:20.820
I'm not ready yet.

21:22.860 --> 21:23.490
All right.

21:23.490 --> 21:24.340
You can go out first.

21:24.340 --> 21:25.670
Leave me alone for a while.

21:25.670 --> 21:26.280
Yes.

21:41.930 --> 21:43.260
You did me a great favor.

21:43.990 --> 21:45.520
Let me treat you to some tea.

21:50.980 --> 21:52.260
It's snowing again.

21:56.300 --> 21:57.650
Why do Changmo and Jinglan

21:57.650 --> 21:59.250
have to fight?

22:00.540 --> 22:01.780
If there were peace,

22:02.210 --> 22:03.470
why would there be war?

22:03.650 --> 22:06.250
Changmo has been attacking
Jinglan all year round.

22:06.250 --> 22:08.900
It's why we built the Tianlang Pass.

22:10.580 --> 22:11.900
But even so,

22:12.250 --> 22:14.180
they still want to attack the city.

22:15.820 --> 22:17.620
You've never lived in Changmo.

22:18.380 --> 22:21.140
Most of the lands beyond the northern
border are deserts.

22:21.140 --> 22:22.870
If there's a natural disaster,

22:23.010 --> 22:24.730
both people and livestock
will starve to death.

22:24.730 --> 22:25.990
If they could survive,

22:26.410 --> 22:28.900
who would risk their lives to fight a war?

22:30.970 --> 22:31.730
What you said

22:32.620 --> 22:33.490
makes sense.

22:37.820 --> 22:39.250
You have been fighting for years.

22:39.250 --> 22:41.170
How could you know
the suffering of us commoners?

22:41.170 --> 22:42.690
Peace is so precious.

22:42.730 --> 22:43.730
I want to know.

22:44.930 --> 22:46.330
Have you stayed by my side

22:47.010 --> 22:48.410
just to treat my illness?

22:48.860 --> 22:50.210
I am a physician.

22:50.350 --> 22:52.210
I need to prove my medical skills.

22:52.490 --> 22:54.690
And you also have to pay my medical fees.

22:55.340 --> 22:56.540
No other reasons?

22:57.820 --> 22:59.220
What else could there be?

23:03.250 --> 23:04.340
Tell me,

23:04.620 --> 23:05.860
how could there be

23:05.860 --> 23:07.790
such a strange thing in this world?

23:08.060 --> 23:10.300
We're good friends who haven't
seen each other for years.

23:10.300 --> 23:12.830
But she didn't recognize me
when we met again.

23:14.780 --> 23:15.580
Yes.

23:17.250 --> 23:18.850
Why didn't she recognize me?

23:19.750 --> 23:22.100
Maybe a fever ruined her brain,

23:22.780 --> 23:24.780
or she accidentally hurt her head,

23:25.540 --> 23:26.970
or she got some kind of

23:26.970 --> 23:28.230
amnesia or something.

23:31.140 --> 23:31.860
Then,

23:32.410 --> 23:33.540
when you were young,

23:33.540 --> 23:35.780
did you hurt your head

23:35.930 --> 23:37.130
and lose your memory?

23:38.450 --> 23:40.170
My second uncle said that
when I was a teenager,

23:40.170 --> 23:41.300
my head was injured.

23:43.860 --> 23:45.540
Then, did you

23:45.860 --> 23:47.490
forget any important friends
due to that?

23:47.490 --> 23:48.700
How is that possible?

23:48.970 --> 23:49.450
I...

23:54.170 --> 23:55.630
Why are you asking so much?

23:55.970 --> 23:56.650
Nothing.

23:56.980 --> 23:57.710
Just asking.

24:01.860 --> 24:03.610
Is it that good?

24:05.570 --> 24:06.300
Let me try it.

24:08.340 --> 24:09.270
Can you drink it?

24:20.860 --> 24:22.410
It doesn't taste that good.

24:25.170 --> 24:26.370
I'm going home first.

24:32.370 --> 24:33.100
Are you okay?

24:42.450 --> 24:43.210
I didn't expect that

24:43.210 --> 24:43.930
you even knew this trick.

24:43.930 --> 24:45.860
I also know grappling techniques.

24:55.140 --> 24:57.140
She really passed out after one sip.

25:06.150 --> 25:07.040
General.

25:09.450 --> 25:10.300
What's up?

25:10.570 --> 25:11.830
She got drunk on water?

25:12.170 --> 25:12.730
She...

25:14.820 --> 25:15.260
She...

25:15.620 --> 25:18.150
She can't even drink
a single drop of alcohol.

25:18.340 --> 25:18.860
Sir,

25:19.100 --> 25:20.300
the banquet is ready.

25:20.450 --> 25:22.980
Lord Fei and Her Highness
are already inside.

25:23.140 --> 25:23.730
Okay.

25:24.290 --> 25:24.850
Tonight,

25:25.010 --> 25:26.060
take your cues from me.

25:26.060 --> 25:26.490
Yes.

25:27.210 --> 25:28.140
There's wine.

25:30.380 --> 25:30.820
You.

25:31.730 --> 25:32.340
Come on.

25:32.540 --> 25:33.670
Watch out.

25:34.140 --> 25:34.740
Slow down.

25:35.140 --> 25:35.820
Slow down.

25:40.170 --> 25:40.690
Zheng.

25:41.170 --> 25:41.770
Princess.

25:41.860 --> 25:42.690
I'm the host tonight.

25:42.690 --> 25:43.420
But I'm late.

25:43.580 --> 25:45.440
Sorry for that. I'll drink first.

25:47.780 --> 25:49.240
After you, Your Highness.

25:54.060 --> 25:55.060
We haven't reached the capital yet.

25:55.060 --> 25:56.340
You've worked hard, Lord Fei.

25:56.340 --> 25:57.370
I offer you a toast.

25:57.370 --> 25:59.010
As the special envoy
for the marriage alliance,

25:59.010 --> 26:00.820
it is my utmost honor.

26:04.210 --> 26:05.650
Visitors from afar are guests.

26:05.650 --> 26:06.620
My Lady,

26:06.970 --> 26:08.970
why don't you toast Lord Fei as well?

26:11.250 --> 26:12.340
That's right, Jin Xi.

26:12.340 --> 26:13.690
Toast Lord Fei too.

26:15.190 --> 26:15.790
Yes.

26:21.060 --> 26:21.590
Lord Fei,

26:22.080 --> 26:23.540
before I offer this toast,

26:23.690 --> 26:25.100
I still want to know

26:25.340 --> 26:27.270
when we can depart for the capital.

26:27.380 --> 26:28.930
I have made it very clear.

26:29.170 --> 26:31.300
We must wait for His Majesty's decree.

26:31.410 --> 26:33.740
What if His Majesty never issues a decree?

26:33.820 --> 26:35.620
Must Her Highness keep waiting?

26:38.410 --> 26:40.340
It seems that is the only way.

26:45.140 --> 26:45.800
Chengfeng,

26:46.170 --> 26:47.300
you're just in time.

26:47.490 --> 26:48.730
Perform a sword dance for everyone

26:48.730 --> 26:49.790
to liven things up.

26:50.220 --> 26:51.420
Yes, General.

27:18.060 --> 27:20.100
Wait, why are you fighting?

27:24.060 --> 27:26.340
Why are you bullying a weak woman?

27:26.820 --> 27:27.480
Chengfeng.

27:27.800 --> 27:28.250
Yes.

27:28.280 --> 27:28.940
Apologize.

27:31.410 --> 27:31.930
Yes.

27:34.100 --> 27:35.100
My Lady,

27:35.490 --> 27:36.250
I

27:36.520 --> 27:37.850
accidentally slipped.

27:37.970 --> 27:38.490
Sorry.

27:40.330 --> 27:41.190
Physician Han.

27:41.470 --> 27:43.650
General Chengfeng has already apologized.

27:43.650 --> 27:45.380
Why don't you take a seat first?

27:47.100 --> 27:48.060
Report!

27:48.910 --> 27:50.540
Ms. Tang requests an audience.

27:50.540 --> 27:51.410
Show them in.

27:51.440 --> 27:51.960
Yes.

27:55.100 --> 27:56.140
Xiao Chi.

27:56.580 --> 27:59.060
Why didn't you invite me
to drink with you?

27:59.410 --> 27:59.940
Ms. Tang.

28:00.140 --> 28:01.200
Please take a seat.

28:02.140 --> 28:03.450
What

28:03.540 --> 28:04.870
brought you here today?

28:05.170 --> 28:05.900
What?

28:06.450 --> 28:08.250
You owe me a romantic debt,

28:08.380 --> 28:09.450
but you're ignoring me now?

28:09.450 --> 28:10.100
Ms. Tang.

28:10.410 --> 28:11.650
Don't talk

28:11.860 --> 28:12.880
nonsense.

28:13.380 --> 28:14.010
I

28:14.140 --> 28:15.690
want to marry Xiao Chi

28:15.930 --> 28:17.660
like all the women in this city.

28:18.010 --> 28:19.100
So, you

28:19.170 --> 28:21.010
owe a romantic debt to all of us.

28:23.210 --> 28:24.010
Ms. Tang,

28:24.490 --> 28:25.620
let me properly introduce you

28:25.620 --> 28:26.950
everyone present here.

28:27.780 --> 28:29.680
This is the Minister of Revenue,

28:30.100 --> 28:31.230
Fei Zheng, Lord Fei.

28:34.210 --> 28:35.970
This is the Princess of Changmo.

28:35.970 --> 28:38.540
Your Highness is indeed a great beauty.

28:39.410 --> 28:41.410
This is Physician Han.

28:42.930 --> 28:43.790
Physician Han.

28:46.380 --> 28:48.900
And this is the famous person
in our Tianlang Pass...

28:48.900 --> 28:50.010
I am Tang Zhaoxue.

28:50.170 --> 28:51.770
All the inns in Tianlang Pass

28:51.900 --> 28:52.820
are run by me.

28:53.270 --> 28:54.030
Zheng.

28:54.820 --> 28:56.650
When there was a famine at Tianlang Pass,

28:56.650 --> 28:57.980
Ms. Tang helped us a lot.

28:59.900 --> 29:01.030
I didn't expect that

29:01.170 --> 29:02.860
Ms. Tang is not only beautiful,

29:02.860 --> 29:03.870
but also very kind.

29:03.870 --> 29:05.550
Then I will be bold enough

29:06.000 --> 29:07.190
to toast you all.

29:11.410 --> 29:12.270
Physician Han.

29:13.730 --> 29:15.390
You'd better not drink today.

29:19.620 --> 29:21.690
The imperial decree has arrived.

29:22.900 --> 29:24.580
The Emperor has issued a decree.

29:24.580 --> 29:27.170
Everyone has to kneel to receive it.

29:28.900 --> 29:30.170
The Emperor commands

29:30.380 --> 29:32.580
that the special envoy
for the marriage alliance, Fei Zheng,

29:32.580 --> 29:35.820
immediately lead the alliance procession
back to the capital.

29:35.820 --> 29:37.300
No delays are allowed.

29:37.650 --> 29:40.650
General Xiao Chi
should escort them personally

29:40.650 --> 29:42.210
and return together.

29:42.210 --> 29:43.730
Respect this.

29:46.900 --> 29:48.580
I receive the decree.
